Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.14,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier 而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.31,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.28,0:00:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕过危险的转角追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.72,0:00:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.66,0:00:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.27,0:00:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.45,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.39,0:01:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.89,0:01:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.13,0:01:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.94,0:01:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻壳机动队 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗手间吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 先等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间内的墙壁和地板全部贴有瓷砖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.05,0:02:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户无法开启外侧还有铝制的格子窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.09,0:02:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她很轻易就能打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 她应该不会干这么粗暴的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#11 草迷宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧 买给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.79,0:02:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用体内反应器分解酒精的人真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这次新人录用测验的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难易度设定会不会搞错了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度都无法突破的话就表示训练生的素质太差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说也没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边喝咖啡一边看报纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是问你 我问的是他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的就是他们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全放松下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许会被假记忆欺骗的念头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们完全没有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点刚开始我就教过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的人数呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3组6名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去下一组咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一组了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 虽然很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.98,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去目标了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来打算怎么办啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想再搜寻一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就加油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不会太冷淡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情他们有什么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会生气先回去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是入侵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有4层防壁被突破的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是训练生干的那可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是终点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么感觉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.47,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤触觉接受器收到的感觉是明确的现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却完全没有现实感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义体吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的店主?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.13,0:08:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想寄放什么东西呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄放?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.23,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里做的生意是寄放客户的外部记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这里的东西全是外人看来没什么价值的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.24,0:08:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但每一件却都装满着拥有者非常多的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我常常会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这些东西散发出来的残留思念感动得喘不过气来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.43,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是被那个吸引到这边来的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以全身义体来说算是非常早期制作的珍贵产品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个孩子身上的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总让我觉得很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.78,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在此同时我也品尝到受托保管他人记忆的快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个孩子之间有什么样的记忆呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.16,0:09:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 已经这么晚了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 今天我要提早关门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有时间的时候请再度光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.37,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,届时我会慢慢把故事说给你听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个奇妙的感觉是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乡愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再跟少校报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要就这样不见人影嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前到哪里去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.59,0:10:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次录用有几个可能过关的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长的朋友推荐进来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陆自情报部出身的男子1名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素质下降虽然是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.00,0:10:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 确保有预备人员的确也是当务之急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是难易度设定如果再降低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会搞得外强中干而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.71,0:10:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天追加测试吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟课长讨论过再决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我适合当训练教官吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.96,0:11:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不适合的话就没人适合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面交给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是来9课之前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分钟就会被少校甩掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.97,0:11:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水准还真低啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要是老大你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.58,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对少校这种突然消失的目标有办法跟踪到最后吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.83,0:11:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白日梦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是更灵异的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.13,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我曾在翻身的时候灵魂出窍看到奇怪的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有在自己的东西上面感受到思念过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长距离开车当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过车子本身好像手脚延长的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在叫小包过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得好好玩一次好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我有件非做不可的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.93,0:12:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来逛昨天的路线做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现我在跟踪她了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你差不多该到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.07,0:13:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这两个孩子已经等不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点告诉我这两个孩子的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是急性子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两具义体以前一直都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.02,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由长大之后的男孩小心保管着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩在6岁的时候遇到飞机事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是大多数乘客都罹难的严重事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被救出来的人也都在短时间内过世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.21,0:13:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个男孩和恰巧坐在他旁边的女孩还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然两人奇迹似的捡回一条命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.66,0:13:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是女孩没有恢复意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩除了左手之外全身完全无法活动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体上的伤恢复之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩很快就明白了自己的处境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是一起搭机的父母双双死亡的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.68,0:14:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是远房亲戚刚开始很亲切地来看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却马上疏远他的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都用那小小的脑袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力的去接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.56,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他把睡在隔壁床跟自己有着同样遭遇的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看作是这世界上唯一的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望她能够醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.64,0:14:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一边这样祈祷边用一只左手拼命折纸鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩出事了 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之后女孩的病情急速恶化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血压60
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有舒张压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注射各一单位的抗心律不整药和强心剂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ECF(细胞外液)不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血压降到40
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上准备手术室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.28,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩听说女孩到很远的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又过了两年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩不跟任何人说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.54,0:15:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是默默的折着纸鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛继续折那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.86,0:16:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上天赋予他的人生重责大任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天说了什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要白色的折纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诉讼等手续全部结束的某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个年轻医生和某个男性亲戚来到医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟男孩这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.01,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.38,0:16:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种治疗法可以换掉你所有不能动的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问他有没有尝试的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.09,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说如果顺利就可以像以前那样正常生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩没有回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.87,0:16:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是男孩提不起勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有想要回到以前那种正常生活的动机啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了继续折纸鹤外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经对任何事情都没有兴趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此周围的大人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.89,0:17:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都放弃说服男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.06,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 有个女孩却创造了开启男孩心扉的契机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是这孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.63,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.97,0:17:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子已经接受全身义体治疗并且获得成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.84,0:17:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是那个年轻医生 认为这是说服男孩的最后手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才将两个人拉在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.48,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩每天都来看男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个非常开朗活泼的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.49,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯全身义体之前应该很难熬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.43,0:17:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她却从没跟男孩诉苦过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.33,0:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但如此 她还一有机会就劝男孩做义体化手术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然男孩一直默默听着不说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天却突然这样对她说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你能用义体折纸鹤吗?”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“如果做得到 要我全身义体化也行”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.66,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她虽然能够用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.13,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还没有办法控制义体做出细致的动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子大概是不认输吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尽办法拼命折着纸鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.74,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对男孩来说那个女孩应该是一种希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.61,0:18:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 两个人都还太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩很失望地说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.81,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能为死去的女孩折纸鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“那我维持现状就好”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩在男孩面前消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下一句 “这次换我为你练习折纸鹤了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是男孩一直以为已经死去的那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她不说出这件事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.11,0:19:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有什么重大的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.65,0:19:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩从那天起就决定自己也要义体化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在心里发誓要去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.66,0:20:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从医院消失的那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.23,0:20:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来男孩也全身义体化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熬过艰苦的复健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.07,0:20:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大成为优秀的义体使用者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.61,0:20:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是个很少有儿童换全身义体的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.51,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是超乎想像的艰苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.18,0:20:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一想到那个女孩也承受过同样的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就能很轻易的熬过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.69,0:20:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他找到那个女孩了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机事故后换成全身义体的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的线索应该已经足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.54,0:20:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是找不到那女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这女孩的义体是在哪里找到的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.91,0:20:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩在大学实验室的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到这个被当成标本保存下来的义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.88,0:21:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩虽然一眼就知道她就是自己寻找的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.39,0:21:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到最后还是找不到更换义体SIZE的女孩本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以女孩这方面的记忆到现在还是空白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩现在人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.00,0:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大战后期出兵到外国就断了消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.51,0:21:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来就再也没来过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你告诉我这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定还在寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次喜欢上的男孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次喜欢上的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.92,0:22:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰红茶的冰块快溶光了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.46,0:22:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说关于那些家伙的测验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重新考虑难易度设定的条件下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.33,0:22:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让他们再测验一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.64,0:22:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是吹什么风啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.31,0:22:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.48,0:22:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得我刚进游击队的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.84,0:22:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾经意外的无法发挥实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.11,0:22:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨长官一顿臭骂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.55,0:22:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想起这件事 所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.85,0:22:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.35,0:22:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实没有人可以—开始就做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.49,0:22:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.73,0:22:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能这么说真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.68,0:23:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.49,0:23:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.96,0:23:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.90,0:23:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.14,0:23:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.74,0:23:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.38,0:23:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我审视自身--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.45,0:23:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.72,0:23:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.09,0:23:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.13,0:24:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.40,0:24:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.40,0:24:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.17,0:24:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我审视自身--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.04,0:24:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.28,0:24:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.72,0:24:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.82,0:24:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个躯壳里

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

